player has ten health and gets 3 more every boss. the player can change weapons upon finding them in different rooms.
the different weapons are wood sword(you start with this), iron sword, diomand sword, rock spear, iron spear, diomand spear, and bow.
spears sacrafice strength for a long reach
rock spear: 2 damage
iron spear: 3 damage
diomand spear: 5 damage
swords have a short reach
wood sword: 3 damage
iron sword: 4 damage
diomand sword: 6 damage
the bow shoots in a straight line in the direction that the player is facing
bow: 3 damage
the player can only have one weapon at a time
or keys[pygame.K_SPACE]or keys[pygame.K_w]